thread.title: Moon turns red in rare eclipse

title: Moon turns red in rare eclipse
text:
Moon turns red in rare eclipse 6:16am IST - 00:30 
Skywatchers across western North America set their alarms to wake before dawn on Wednesday to see a rare type of lunar eclipse called a ''Super Blue Blood Moon.'' Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
